{"tid":99456,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【侵帝】朱克伯格質疑特朗普限移民令政策","createTime":"2017-01-29T08:24:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-29T15:53:26.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a6667ce604d230e1bb85bb811decd1b9e1c86cdc","tid":99456,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T08:24:45.000Z","msg":"特朗普限移民令惹混亂　持「綠卡」也被拒入境　FB朱克伯格公開質疑政策 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/MarkZuckerberg-TRUMP_WCK1E_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FMarkZuckerberg-TRUMP_WCK1E_1200x0.png&h=3e12ecbe&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n特朗普剛剛簽署的針對7個穆斯林國家的「入境禁令」已經生效。即使持美國綠卡的人也暫時無法回到美國。此舉引起廣泛批評，伊朗宣稱要實施報復。 <br />\n<br />\n德國之聲報道，美國總統特朗普週五（1月27日）簽署的政令「阻止外國恐怖分子進入美國的國家保護計劃」週六開始生效。其涉及範圍廣泛，即使沒有犯罪記錄或恐怖主義背景的移民也將被阻擋在美國國門之外。 <br />\n<br />\n一些美國名人對特朗普的政令公開提出質疑。facebook創始人朱克伯格（Mark Zuckerberg）表示，他的祖父母來自德國、奧地利和波蘭，他妻子的父母，是中國和越南移民，「美國是一個移民國家，我們應該為此感到驕傲&hellip;&hellip;我們需要維持這個國家的安全，但是我們應該聚焦那些真正構成威脅的人。」 <br />\n<br />\n目前這份政令主要波及難民以及大批來自穆斯林國家的移民。敘利亞難民將被全面禁止入境美國，此外在未來120天內，伊朗、伊拉克、也門、利比亞、蘇丹和索馬里公民一律不予簽發美國簽證，只有持外交護照者和國際組織的工作人員除外。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E9%99%90%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E4%BB%A4%E6%83%B9%E6%B7%B7%E4%BA%82-%E6%8C%81-%E7%B6%A0%E5%8D%A1-%E4%B9%9F%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%92%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83-fb%E6%9C%B1%E5%85%8B%E4%BC%AF%E6%A0%BC%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E9%2599%2590%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E6%2583%25B9%25E6%25B7%25B7%25E4%25BA%2582-%25E6%258C%2581-%25E7%25B6%25A0%25E5%258D%25A1-%25E4%25B9%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258B%2592%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25A2%2583-fb%25E6%259C%25B1%25E5%2585%258B%25E4%25BC%25AF%25E6%25A0%25BC%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2596%258B%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%2594%25BF%25E7%25AD%2596%2F&d=Nf8hSSvrm%2BrnvpkhsUeGbAv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=bfa7ae43\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E9%2599%2590%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E6%2583%25B9%25E6%25B7%25B7%25E4%25BA%2582-%25E6%258C%2581-%25E7%25B6%25A0%25E5%258D%25A1-%25E4%25B9%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258B%2592%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25A2%2583-fb%25E6%259C%25B1%25E5%2585%258B%25E4%25BC%25AF%25E6%25A0%25BC%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2596%258B%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%2594%25BF%25E7%25AD%2596%2F&h=01b50505\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E9%99%90%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E4%BB%A4%E6%83%B9%E6%B7%B7%E4%BA%82-%E6%8C%81-%E7%B6%A0%E5%8D%A1-%E4%B9%9F%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%92%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83-fb%E6%9C%B1%E5%85%8B%E4%BC%AF%E6%A0%BC%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96/</a>"},{"pid":"ed6549fbd7e31399ee1fbaabbc14a4485157fa1b","tid":99456,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T08:27:20.000Z","msg":"打亂種"},{"pid":"8df654bf5129993eda688a219024ac1c5a95539b","tid":99456,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T08:34:20.000Z","msg":"收皮啦奶共狗"},{"pid":"ea8171cb1e279b4ea326c677e09e18a5dd4647fe","tid":99456,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T08:36:34.000Z","msg":"佢老婆真係狗都唔屌"},{"pid":"92802c09b74259907e54f141c2838e5edb957b07","tid":99456,"uid":498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T08:37:03.000Z","msg":"豬西伯格你人所共知係奶共共碟黎<br />\n我係美國政府就叫國稅局搞鳩你"},{"pid":"089cbe73bab0c16948070f6ce78deeb357d5d973","tid":99456,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T08:38:02.000Z","msg":"移民國家唔等於乜嘢狗屎垃圾都要收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbd3ad457fa8460a1da37b0c005aff068915b0e0","tid":99456,"uid